      "comment": "SHEZ SWEET LOUISE NZ (8) returns from a stint in Brisbane where she scored a win two back at Albion Park. May need a bit of luck negotiating a very wide starting position but she is a capable mare who owns a good record at this circuit and distance. BABY YOUR THE ONE (6) is another returning from Queensland where she scored two back at Albion Park. Her strike rate at this circuit and distance is encouraging. ALFNALMA (7) is up in grade on the last-start win and draws wider but loves this shorter distance, recording four wins and a placing in five tries at it here.. ALWAYSBMYPONY (9) has been racing well of late, recording a string of top-four results since coming from the back row to win at this venue last month. Draws for a trail so can feature again.",
